.0618, 143.5953, 143.0851, 142.6801, 143.3962, 145.4175, 145.4974, 145.299, 145.356, 144.3971, 145.1615, 144.9942, 145.7935, 145.359, 144.7357, 144.9617, 145.308, 145.6223, 144.4727, 144.4412, 143.6681, 144.1106, 143.9329, 145.8188, 144.9936, 146.1908, 147.2109, 146.6794, 148.3431, 146.2687, 144.9253, 145.1849, 143.9383, 143.8157, 145.3508, 143.7873, 143.2513, 143.0661, 142.3087, 142.7703, 140.2585, 139.723, 141.3771, 139.0072, 135.9761, 137.4031, 137.4989, 136.5217, 138.5268, 137.7077, 136.4119, 136.9838, 136.9069, 137.8334, 137.7285, 136.5859, 135.3637, 136.7601, 137.3042, 138.5607, 138.8742, 139.0566, 138.2251, 137.9876, 138.1638, 138.8725, 140.2471, 141.1553, 142.122, 142.9246, 144.4039, 146.052, 145.0048, 145.1768, 145.325, 145.7671, 146.0076, 145.1423, 145.2564, 144.8445, 143.6783, 143.0514, 144.34, 143.6268, 145.4888, 144.1818, 144.5194, 145.2781, 144.6117, 144.2207, 143.8084, 139.7462, 139.5699, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>量价因子之单因子测试 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.11)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告系统测试了四大类量价因子（规模、换手率、成交量/成交额、动量）在A股沪深300和中证500股票池中的单因子有效性。核心发现是换手率和成交量因子与收益率呈强负相关（流动性溢价），动量因子呈短期反转效应。</p>\n<p>在商品期货上复现时，两个因子表现最突出：(1) Amihud非流动性因子（正向：高非流动性品种获得流动性溢价）；(2) 252日动量延续因子（正向：商品趋势延续性强于股票）。两者等权组合后在21日持有期下Sharpe达1.11，体现了流动性溢价与趋势动量的互补性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.73</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.01</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3198</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.97</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.57</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.36 / 0.57</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td>1.03</td><td>0.24</td><td>0.77</td><td>1.4</td><td>1.41</td><td>0.73</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.49</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.68</span></td><td>1.49</td><td>0.05</td><td>0.06</td><td>0.46</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.47</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 63 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 63 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3200</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>94.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>37.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Amihud非流动性</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Illiquidity}_t = \\frac{1}{20}\\sum_{i=0}^{19}\\frac{|r_{t-i}|}{\\text{Amount}_{t-i}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">r_{t}</span> 为日收益率，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Amount}_{t}</span> 为日成交额。</p>\n<p><strong>252日动量</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Mom252}_t = \\frac{P_t}{P_{t-252}} - 1</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Signal}_t = \\frac{\\text{CRank}(\\text{Illiquidity}_t) + \\text{CRank}(\\text{Mom252}_t)}{2}</div>\n<p>截面百分位排名后映射为连续信号 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, +1]</span>，再经 vol-target 缩放。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>12个因子全部实现，illiquidity最佳(0.46)，换手率/成交量/动量反转因子Sharpe为负</td><td>忠实于报告实现全部因子，统一21日持有期</td><td>best=0.464, 发现负向因子在商品上不如股票</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>尝试双向(正/负)因子，发现commodity momentum应为正向(continuation而非reversal)</td><td>加入momentum continuation、多hold period、IC gate</td><td>best=0.391(下降)，hold=10过短导致换手率0.93</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>聚焦illiquidity+momentum组合，拉长hold period，vol_target grid</td><td>illiq+mom120 combo H42达0.892，mom252单因子0.889</td><td><strong>best=0.892, 首次通过</strong></td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>探索illiq+mom252组合，启用cs/ts归一化，细化参数grid</td><td>illiq+mom252 combo H21=1.111，多个变体&gt;0.8</td><td><strong>best=1.111, 显著提升</strong></td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R3发现252日动量(年度动量continuation)在商品期货上极强，与illiquidity互补性好。R4确认illiq+mom252组合在21-63日hold period内均稳健。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约69-72个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 21-63日（月度至季度调仓）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 报告原文针对A股，商品期货上换手率/成交量因子的负向效应弱化\n<p>- 2021年和2023年Sharpe为负（约-0.17和-0.04），存在阶段性失效 - Amihud illiquidity依赖amount字段质量，部分品种amount数据不完整 - 252日动量需要较长预热期（1年数据）</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.24s</li>\n</ul>"}